title: ATT profit beats estimates raises full-year forecast
text:
AT&T profit beats estimates, raises full-year forecast 
Times Of India Friday 23rd October, 2015 
As the US wireless market stagnates, AT&T is seeking new revenue streams and betting on DirecTV's satellite TV business to help beef up its bundles of cellular, broadband, TV and fixed-line phone services....
